&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated track record of building a compliance certification program from scratch, in-depth knowledge of compliance and regula

&lt;h4&gt;About M0&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;M0 is the modular stablecoin infrastructure. It gives businesses everything they need to launch a stablecoin built around their product, with separate, configurable layers for application, distribution, and issuance. Choose your regulated issuer, with the option to switch them later. Design how your stablecoin behaves with templates and custom logic. Tap shared liquidity across the network from day one. Other stablecoin platforms bundle every layer into a single fixed stack. M0 keeps them independent, so your stablecoin stays yours.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Who we’re looking for&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;M0 is looking for a Lead Brand Designer to push the brand into a new, formative era.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As Lead Brand Designer, you will report directly to the Creative Director and play a key role in defining, differentiating, and scaling the M0 identity across all surfaces, including but not limited to web, campaigns, print, and digital experiences. The ideal candidate will have expertise translating highly complex and technical products and services into strategically compelling and emotionally resonant visual work. You’re exceptionally conceptual, experimental, and iterative — not afraid to learn new things, dive into the deep end, or frolic through your creative mind coming up with striking ideas that push boundaries industry-wide.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;What you’ll do&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Define and evolve M0’s visual identity.&lt;/strong&gt; Ensure a differentiated presence in the market while expanding the brand’s art direction and design system with strategically sound consistency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Execute sharp design work.&lt;/strong&gt; This is a role for makers. You know how to execute against briefs and produce thoughtful, smart work on tight timelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Concept and execute campaign work.&lt;/strong&gt; Collaborate closely with the CD to ideate through compelling campaign constructions from concept to final assets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Create adaptive toolkits&lt;/strong&gt; that teams can use for routine self-service content that evolves with the brand.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Produce sales and developer materials.&lt;/strong&gt; One-sheeters, diagrams for dev docs, event banners, slide decks. You get the gist.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leverage AI tools strategically.&lt;/strong&gt; Not as a crutch. Use innovative tools to enhance operational efficiency, not as a replacement for human-grade creativity and ingenuity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborate across the organization.&lt;/strong&gt; Work closely with copywriters, marketing, product, BD, and external agencies to produce cutting-edge, on-brand work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stay current on creative, advertising, and industry trends, along with culture and emerging technologies&lt;/strong&gt; to inspire fresh, forward-thinking work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
