&lt;p&gt;M0 is seeking an experienced and exceptionally sharp corporate lawyer to be a key player in our growth. Beyond being a pragmatic lawyer with a proven track record of executing complex deals, this team member should be a creative legal strategist, a true business partner. You will execute on M0&#39;s most important commercial and corporate legal work in a deeply cross-functional environment.&lt;/p&gt;
