&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own Day-to-Day Legal Execution&lt;/strong&gt;: Serve as the in-house point of contact across a wide swathe of commercial, corporate, and operational legal matters, working closely with all key senior decision makers at M0.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead Strategic Transactions&lt;/strong&gt;: Act as the Legal lead on M&amp;amp;A, investments, joint ventures, and other strategic corporate initiatives, structuring and executing these complex deals from diligence to closing.&lt;/li&gt;
